g.text: Color Changing ShapesThere is a shape which provides color changing abilites to third party shapes.
Value Displaying ShapesThere are shapes which display a value or use the a value to hide/show other shapes.
Status ImagesStatus images show different images depending on the status of an value.
Sparkline, Area, Bar and Donut ChartsSparklines and area charts allow the visualization of data over time and the donut and bar charts visualizes the relationship between several values.
FeedShows a RSS like feed in your dashboard.
List of ElementsShows a feed of sub-dashboards.
Web PageShows a web page on top of the dashboard.
